Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全身都是泡泡啊
