Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:50.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}静かに燃える世界　始まりはここから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:54.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}夜空が終わりを告げるとき
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:01:00.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}ひとすじの光が　胸に秘めた声が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:04.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}解き放つ　闇を裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:09.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}枯れるよりいっそ　散り急ぐ姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:14.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迷い　歩く術を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:22.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}千の波に　呑まれた心じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}君さえ守れない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:30.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}響け確かな衝動　鳴り止まぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:35.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忘れられぬ傷を残して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:40.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今もかすかな残像　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:45.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}世界が待ってる　明日の産声を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:50.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}響け確かな衝動　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:58.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}そう未来と過去が交差する　百年目の歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【OPCN】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:50.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一切都始于这个静静地燃烧着的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:54.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在长夜将明的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:01:00.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一道光芒 一声发自灵魂的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:04.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}冲破束缚 撕裂黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:09.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}寻求着归宿的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:14.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迷茫地迈足前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:22.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这颗被波涛掩去的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}甚至没法保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:30.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}心脏在胸中激荡 就像要跳出来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:35.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}留下无法忘却的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:40.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}希望这微弱的残影 永远不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:45.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}世界正在等待 属于明日的婴啼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:50.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}心脏在胸中激荡 千万不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:58.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的 这是一首交错着过去与未来的百年长歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}标记的位置就是目击过武藏号的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她们打算去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我觉得她们是想靠近本土吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}学校叫我们去追武藏号来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在通讯无碍 而且能接受调遣的好像只有我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或许就像美波同学说得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家是不是都被那老鼠一样的东西弄得不正常了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在我们也只能在这片海域展开搜索了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无法确认故障原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水箱应该已经修过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概有什么地方还在漏水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能请求补给了 舰…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五天后才能和补给舰会合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那之前只能节约用水了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小幸 你能去看看气象图吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}渴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就喝弹珠汽水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喝腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会喝胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.05,Post upright,,0,0,0,,{\c&H383838&\frz281.9\3c&HF1F1F1&\move(232,362,236,-102)}水可是很珍贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:22.43,Post,,0,0,0,,{\c&H383838&\3c&HF1F1F1&\frz11.75\move(654,584,658,132)}各位同学请节约用水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什么菜不用水就能做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}厕所怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不会吧 难道不准用了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}冲厕所用的是海水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}买了那么多厕纸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是谁放的盐水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.92,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}给我出来 到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你听说小黑那件事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.41,Post upright,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\bord0\c&H383838&\move(754,408,754,498)}今天开始淋浴与泡澡\N\N\N\N\N\N将使用海水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三天没洗了 洗还是不洗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们的头发怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就像爆炸头一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}头发可是女孩子的命根
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水煮鲭鱼 水煮番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什锦蔬菜 压缩饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一堆罐装食品 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别那么挑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唉 没办法 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是下场雨就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我快到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不想让内裤沾上海水的咸味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不爱喝碳酸饮料吗 小…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃 那个 前方有雾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小聪 打开探照灯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小幸 鸣雾笛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样根本没法收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好不容易才接到一点雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撤退 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是个大型低气压
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 借一步说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:32.59,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}暴雨天气 禁止前往上层甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.93,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}重复一遍 禁止前往上层甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能走甲板还真是不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(238,700)}然后呢 她的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(962,700)}今天的晚饭是什么呢 我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你先请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真挤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}岬同学 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去找个人代班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要啊 帅死我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.25,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你对我家真知知做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.24,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.40,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你叫我怎么冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:30.33,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我要办了她 你给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要拿下你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「跟拔蛀牙一样」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「轻而易举」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这句真是经典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常之赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么要在我房间看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我房间没电视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长你看不看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}免了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是这一段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长 这么晚打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:08:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 能代我班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「咋了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「张嘴说话啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}外边太响了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「什么」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「张嘴说话啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雷声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「是吗 没办法」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「咱去去就回」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「岂能轻易拜了下风」 哗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很困了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这么怕打雷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雷公又不会偷走肚脐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.31,Remark,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}注：日本传说雷公会偷走小孩的肚脐。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我怕的不是打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会想起过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位乘客 本船已发送求救信号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在蓝色人鱼赶来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请保持冷静 听从救援人员的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:00.03,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}水涨上来了 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.60,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妈妈 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明乃 快点跳下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妈妈呢 他们怎么不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是我能早点跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸妈妈或许就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 有求救信号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁发出的求救信号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新桥商店街船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全长135m 总吨位14000t
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舷倾侧 好像是进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乘员有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总乘员552名 现在正在避难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}附近还有船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们距离最近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}联系蓝人总部和学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是航海舰晴风号舰长 岬明乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们是新桥 在法拉洛普岛东南13海里处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}15分钟前 在航行时撞上了暗礁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在船体中央依然挂在暗礁上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有人受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}十人轻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}进水了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舷应该是进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}起火了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白了 我舰大约50分钟后可以抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那之前请船长您继续引导避难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小铃 加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全体听令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乌利西环礁附近有船只触礁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本舰将前往营救此船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}准备海难救援
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}炮雷科及航海科的非执勤人员请立即开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟啦糟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吓死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天气晴朗 不过风大浪高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风暴过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}低气压往西边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倾斜角度约为40度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超过50度时很可能就会倾覆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是新桥的船内地图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前三层都是商店 四层是居住分区
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}中央是舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做好救援准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也开跳艇…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这个舰长又打算擅离职守吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}作为舰长 这种时候该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有点不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长就待在船上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁去指挥救援队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 那我在船上指挥你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 明娜 加上炮雷科的三个人登船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}潜水队入海确认船体受损情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}航海科与急救员引导登上救生艇的人去晴风号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}初中时就接受过无数次救援训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过实际操作还是头一回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我总是不走运 不会出问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说话要看场合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}点亮探照灯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们已经抵达现场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甲板上都是人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甲板交给急救员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去搜救船内的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开始救援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.25,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}救援的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}首先应该清点人数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}识别手环呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}应该先清点伤患吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是带指导手册来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是晴风号副舰长宗谷真白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在开始搜救船内幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居住分区好像还有人 麻烦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}洒水器没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}应急系统被撞坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这艘船…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:14:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船体四号分区前约有一百二十米长的裂纹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前面的三个分区好像已经进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是宗谷 新桥的紧急系统出故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}立刻与新桥接舷 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}注意避开环礁 立刻把船上的人引导到甲板上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}避难引导马上就能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多闻丸不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回过神来的时候就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他还很小吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还没搜查的只有五号分区饮食街了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们去找多闻丸 你们先去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}避难引导成功结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}进去的救援队也都出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:15:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是副舰长和明娜同学好像还在船尾方面继续搜救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}据说有个小孩不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去找这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫找那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多闻丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他还很小…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来说的是猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 新桥要沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}解开称人结
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全速撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彻底断两半了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 副舰长和明娜同学好像还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事情大条了 事情大条了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到了 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小娜 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明娜 跑快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫不正跑着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们减速 你跳下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长 副舰长 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船体中央裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样下去船会沉的 快点出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们接回了明娜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还没找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}联系不上她了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也很怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为我总是不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能坐着等死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等待原来这么痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我和小白已经说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给避难人员发毛毯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另外准备一些吃的 还有热饮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都还在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}航海科的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和避难人员一起回晴风号了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只剩副舰长一个了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是蓝色人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是蓝色人鱼紧急响应舰队的岸间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们是晴风号炮雷科的小笠原光救援队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦各位了 剩下的交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船上还有一个学生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救援对象 一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}避难人员都吃上饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有伤员的话报告给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喝粥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有年糕豆汤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还是这么不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有探测到…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给我锤子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 救援舰说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在蓝色人鱼正在搜救副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}发现救援对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}周边一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}千万别乱动 我们马上进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}活着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们得救了喵 真是太好了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么要学猫叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功救出多闻丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多闻丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多闻丸 你该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它很喜欢你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 多闻丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你来照顾它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你不嫌弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻烦各位了 请把它转交横须贺女子海洋学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另外还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抗体及其个人使用报告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我等你的时候一直很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还以为会把你永远留在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宗谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船上能不能再挤一只？舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}专业蓝人不愧是专业的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以前我遇难的时候也被她们救过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才想做蓝色人鱼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且我觉得上了船以后 或许就能有家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我妈妈以前是蓝色人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她说 海上的伙伴们就像一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我和明明成为蓝色人鱼之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定能得到一个大家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我们做个约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你才总是说 海上的伙伴们都是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个叫萌香的就是武藏号的舰长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫和我们舰长西娅 也是初中以来的老交情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}病毒的抗体已经做好了 好想快点去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:24.94,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,531.333)}多灾多难的暴雨之夜
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:31.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:37.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}言葉よりも優しく　背中を押すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:43.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}そう　私と君のripple effect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:23:00.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}果てなく向かってくる波は険しいばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:06.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}航路はどうしよう　君と選ぶ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:13.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}微笑み忘れたら　私が笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:21.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}涙弾けたあとは　強さが水面に広がるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:30.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:34.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}言葉よりも優しく波打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.77,0:23:38.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}晴れた空とあの風と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:44.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}誰かのそばで　夢を描くのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:48.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その誰かが私でありたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:53.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\3c&HD7C392&\c&HFAF7EF&}きっと春が待ってくれてるから
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【EDCN】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:31.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}青色七洋 今天也环绕着这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:37.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}我会比话语还要温柔 轻轻地推着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:43.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}是啊 这就是你和我之间的涟漪效应
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:23:00.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}面前的惊涛骇浪 一浪卷来一浪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:06.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们选择的航路 就是我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:13.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}如果你忘记了微笑 我会笑给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:21.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}流过眼泪之后 让坚强随波布散
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:30.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}青色七洋 今天也环绕着这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:34.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}比话语还要温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.77,0:23:38.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}是这片晴空和习习凉风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:44.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如果你希望有人能陪你一起描绘梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:48.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我希望我就是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:53.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\3c&HD7C392&\c&HFAF7EF&}要相信春天正在等待着我们
